                     <binding when="1977-01" contemporary="false">
                        <p>Band frá janúar 1977 (<dimensions type="binding" unit="mm">
                              <height>158</height>
                              <width>124</width>
                              <depth>24</depth>
                           </dimensions>). Pappaspjöld klædd fínofnum líndúk. Grófari dúkur á kili
